parts.text:
Yes! I worked as a **Freelance Designer** for the Pac-12 Conference from October 2011 to October 2013. During that time, I:

- Designed the PAC-12 Football Championship logo
- Designed the "12" numeral for the PAC-12 logo (during their expansion from 10 to 12 teams)
- Designed the PAC-12 Women's Basketball Championship logo

This was around the time the conference expanded to include my alma mater, the University of Oregon.
